      "content": "### KEY_FACTORS (top 3)\n1. **Lack of a strongly basic, protonated center at pH 7.4** (aniline-like NH2 / aromatic N\u2019s are weak bases).  \n2. **Compact, rigid fused heteroaromatic scaffold** (less ability to adopt hERG-favorable binding conformations).  \n3. **Only one main aromatic/hydrophobic \u201cflank\u201d** (\u2013OCF3 increases lipophilicity but doesn\u2019t create the classic dual-aromatic cation-flanked motif).",
